data.message: Comprehensive Duro competitive analysis - 5 parallel research agents analyzing 60+ products: Identified unique Duro moat: structured learning (episodes/evaluations/decisions), reputation-based autonomy, debug gates, local-first. Top threats: Mem0 ($24M, AWS), Zep (temporal), Claude Memory. No competitor combines orchestration + learning + local-first. Strategic recommendation: position on learning loops and local ownership.
